---
title: Premium Feast Apricot-Mustard Glazed Salmon with Thyme-Butter Potato Wedges and Peach-Cucumber Salad
description: Sweet and savoury apricot-mustard glazed salmon is the showstopper of this balanced feast. Paired with thyme-butter roasted potatoes and a refreshing salad of arugula-spinach mix, peaches, crisp cucumbers and do-it-yourself croutons, this meal is truly the definition of "summer vibes."
